[{"id":740578,"node":"2020","node_url":"https://www.v2ex.com/go/2020","node_image":"/static/img/node_default_mini.png","description":"<p>“迷乱”</p>\n<p>今年真的过的很迷乱，从年初到年底根本不知道咋过来的，感觉今年是过得最快最紧张的一年。希望明年能好一些。</p>\n","url":"https://www.v2ex.com/t/740578","replies":321,"created_ts":1609386953,"created":"11:55:53","title":"一个词总结一下我的 2020","author":"xutao881","author_url":"https://www.v2ex.com/u/xutao881","author_image":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/61fc/c6a0/356901_mini.png?m=1545789791"},{"id":740606,"node":"问与答","node_url":"https://www.v2ex.com/go/qna","node_image":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/c20a/d4d7/12_mini.png?m=1594743680","description":"<p>这个标题起源于今天的午睡，半睡半醒之间，突然一个名字蹦了出来。源于很久之前看过的一部小说，觉得这个名字这么长时间还没忘的原因就是这个招数名字起得漂亮\n—————— 青莲剑歌。</p>\n<p>想问问大家有没有觉得什么很拉风 NB 的武功招数啥的。。了解一下。</p>\n","url":"https://www.v2ex.com/t/740606","replies":124,"created_ts":1609393179,"created":"13:39:39","title":"你看过的武侠或者玄幻里你觉得说出来最拉风 NB 的招数或者功法","author":"xuewuchen","author_url":"https://www.v2ex.com/u/xuewuchen","author_image":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/bc8b/a5a7/436106_mini.png?m=1567132247"},{"id":740630,"node":"程序员","node_url":"https://www.v2ex.com/go/programmer","node_image":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/94f6/d7e0/300_mini.png?m=1609151647","description":"<p>已经 6500 个 star 了，从法律上来说，这种开源工具构成违法吗？</p>\n","url":"https://www.v2ex.com/t/740630","replies":106,"created_ts":1609395925,"created":"14:25:25","title":"GitHub 上的抢茅台工具，作者会被请去喝茶吗。","author":"Junzhou","author_url":"https://www.v2ex.com/u/Junzhou","author_image":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/bc7c/3ca9/367160_mini.png?m=1595814683"},{"id":740635,"node":"分享发现","node_url":"https://www.v2ex.com/go/share","node_image":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/c74d/97b0/16_mini.png?m=1608830203","description":"<p>感谢党，感谢国家，“感谢”之前为此喋喋不休的网友们</p>\n<p><img alt=\"img\" class=\"embedded_image\" loading=\"lazy\" referrerpolicy=\"no-referrer\" rel=\"noreferrer\" src=\"https://ftp.bmp.ovh/imgs/2020/12/2d9a6c85db3cc99e.png\"/></p>\n<p><a href=\"https://ftp.bmp.ovh/imgs/2020/12/2d9a6c85db3cc99e.png\" rel=\"nofollow\">https://ftp.bmp.ovh/imgs/2020/12/2d9a6c85db3cc99e.png</a></p>\n","url":"https://www.v2ex.com/t/740635","replies":100,"created_ts":1609396698,"created":"14:38:18","title":"新冠疫苗免费了","author":"Huelse","author_url":"https://www.v2ex.com/u/Huelse","author_image":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/6310/dfed/365483_mini.png?m=1583734720"},{"id":740580,"node":"程序员","node_url":"https://www.v2ex.com/go/programmer","node_image":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/94f6/d7e0/300_mini.png?m=1609151647","description":"<p>坐标西安，在某国企混日子，朝九晚六不加班。收入不高不低，以前没买房，感觉还行，买了房后感觉到有点牙利，收入有点不够，所有打算年后跳出来。父母的意思是呆在里面，慢慢熬着，工资慢慢就上来了，如果出来了就不好再回去了。而我现在在刷题打算年后跑路，目前收到几个不错的面试邀请，都约在年后。</p>\n<p>现在有两个问题想咨询下：1.到底要不要跳出来，我是比较倾向跳出来，但不知道怎么说服父母。有没有从国企跳出来的老哥指点下。2.在刷面经的时候，发现很多公司会问项目经历和项目中遇到的难点还有是怎么克服的，碰到这种问题该怎么回答好呢？因为公司原因，我做的项目都是一些政府平台的改造项目，没啥难度，基本都差不多，都是些增删改查。像我这种情况有没有人指点下我该怎么回答呢？</p>\n","url":"https://www.v2ex.com/t/740580","replies":92,"created_ts":1609387021,"created":"11:57:01","title":"目前在国企当程序员，打算年后跳出来，想咨询点问题，有没有人帮忙指点下","author":"AFK092","author_url":"https://www.v2ex.com/u/AFK092","author_image":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/05004d2d8f6fb8ea00e7eb83d25ee7dc?s=24&d=retro"},{"id":740625,"node":"程序员","node_url":"https://www.v2ex.com/go/programmer","node_image":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/94f6/d7e0/300_mini.png?m=1609151647","description":"<p>看到不少同事会穿拖鞋，就是办公区放一双拖鞋，上班的时候换上。我感觉这样还挺舒服的，就是不知道大家怎么看。</p>\n","url":"https://www.v2ex.com/t/740625","replies":77,"created_ts":1609395361,"created":"14:16:01","title":"大家如何看待在办公区穿拖鞋？仅限 IT 行业","author":"hhyvs111","author_url":"https://www.v2ex.com/u/hhyvs111","author_image":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/7c2b/3967/331057_mini.png?m=1587870324"},{"id":740676,"node":"职场话题","node_url":"https://www.v2ex.com/go/career","node_image":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/4ea0/6fbc/770_mini.png?m=1608179815","description":"","url":"https://www.v2ex.com/t/740676","replies":74,"created_ts":1609400856,"created":"15:47:36","title":"大家的年终奖到手了吗？还是要等到农历年再发？","author":"rakuking","author_url":"https://www.v2ex.com/u/rakuking","author_image":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/58bc21a45ad1b62b4f717a58ec617019?s=24&d=retro"},{"id":740754,"node":"生活","node_url":"https://www.v2ex.com/go/life","node_image":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/6e27/13a6/557_mini.png?m=1608969785","description":"洗衣机是装在阳台的，洗衣机结冰了，接口处破裂了。房东说是你自己不会修，不属于机器故障，不会给你修的（合同上说好有故障 3 天内修）。我在外面搞了 1 个多小时，超级冷手冻得通红，前两天已经感冒了，头非常晕坐下来都感觉身体有化学物体在震。而且身上的衣服又擦一大块脏了，已经好几天没洗衣服了，我又有洁癖。房东就是扯皮，电话我直接哭了。我妈平常就超级软弱她说自己找人修，我晚上都 910 点回家也不可能找到人帮我修，随便找个老人我自己也修不好（研究了一天了）他们肯定也修不好，冬天羽绒服自己洗根本洗不动吸了水和石头一样，我住在顶楼没有电梯，要是把衣服送洗衣房，我也没办法克服路途的遥远和一大堆衣服的重量。主要是我腰不好，最近才稍微正常一点。<br />一想到要抱着这种噩梦睡觉，第二天也没有解决办法我就很想哭呜呜","url":"https://www.v2ex.com/t/740754","replies":73,"created_ts":1609415539,"created":"19:52:19","title":"心态崩了求开导","author":"unii23i","author_url":"https://www.v2ex.com/u/unii23i","author_image":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/e3c5/0efb/142283_mini.png?m=1444700263"},{"id":740716,"node":"分享创造","node_url":"https://www.v2ex.com/go/create","node_image":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/70ef/df2e/17_mini.png?m=1596015931","description":"送 50 个永久专业版兑换码，如果你喜欢，辛苦给个好评呗～<br /><br /><a target=\"_blank\" href=\"https://apps.apple.com/cn/app/id1511470343\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\">https://apps.apple.com/cn/app/id1511470343</a><br /><br />MJFTWFM3KR97<br />3MMXXPPKM3NL<br />RY43P4J4X9PT<br />WYTTETE74NA7<br />EW7TJEW7R3PY<br />4YAMHMMF3JFJ<br />T4PF7HFRF6PR<br />F63TWYNEPAM3<br />LKXAKXJ4XLRY<br />7Y4JF4W9KMF3<br />TFWPRYYRHY4W<br />7Y6L6AH6N6NY<br />H3E7RYM6XHL9<br />Y3WNEY4WJN9P<br />4NP7YR9A3E7F<br />ARLHTA4LHPWM<br />XJ9P347RENWT<br />PM9LPKEK7HFL<br />6ARKFNM9FW6A<br />3PNELT9RLR4L<br />FNRMPMKJTHK3<br />TA6MWP44N4PF<br />EWF3HW6XE6XK<br />MHWNWT4Y4XMX<br />YKW6PPJHELMX<br />NM9JFK43NK6X<br />767WLYFF6WHL<br />LTAFYRXAH3LX<br />37KYKRE4HKNP<br />7MJXM9RKK76P<br />7JWYH9RNAHPR<br />WTR4YKPAAJKY<br />TRLW7MNAX6JX<br />RX3Y7PHJRL34<br />3NLN4ENAJ4NL<br />MKT73LHKAHMX<br />R44NNRLXEPJY<br />YX9NMHAHHNWY<br />KRLMNTJ3EWYF<br />F74TX